-- Chrysler says May U.S. sales down 47 percent
-- 
-- Tue Jun 2, 2009 3:48pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2009/06/02/us-chrysler-sales-sb-idUSTRE55167020090602

 

 (Reuters) - Chrysler says its May U.S. sales are down 47 percent. 

 * Chrysler says May US retail sales down 30 percent * Chrysler says May was the best retail sales month of 2009 with 74,741 retail units sold * Chrysler says offering zero percent financing for 60 months through on some 2009 model vehicles, or up to $4,000 consumer cash (Detroit Equities, 313 967 1900)